## Summary
This documentation details how to integrate Amplitude cohorts with LiveRamp's data connectivity platform using three methods: SFTP, Amazon S3, and Snowflake, enabling businesses to transfer and activate audience cohorts for cross-channel marketing and analytics purposes.

